  "title": "HR Manager (Talent Acquisition) - healthcare  #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>HR Manager (Talent Acquisition)</strong> - healthcare <br />📍<strong>Queenstown</strong><br />💼 <strong>Permanent Role</strong><br />💰 <strong>Up to $7,500</strong><br />👥 <strong>Lead a team of 8 recruiters</strong><br />📊 <strong>High-volume, strategic hiring role</strong></p><h3>🔑 <strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><p>• Lead, coach, and performance-manage a team of 8<br />• Co-develop and execute <strong>strategic talent acquisition plans</strong><br />• Drive <strong>operational excellence</strong> across recruitment processes<br />• Analyze recruitment metrics and present insights to senior management<br />• Continuously improve hiring strategies using industry best practices<br />• Partner closely with stakeholders (Hiring Managers, Agencies, Institutes, etc.)</p><h3>🎓 <strong>Requirements</strong></h3><p>✅ Min Bachelor’s Degree<br />✅ <strong>Min. 10 years</strong> Talent Acquisition experience<br /></p><h3>⭐ <strong>Why This Role?</strong></h3><p>✔ Senior leadership exposure<br />✔ Stable <strong>institution </strong><br />✔ Meaningful work supporting healthcare </p><p>📩 <strong>Interested or know someone suitable?</strong><br />submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)<br />Company EA Licence number : 99C4599<br />Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
